column5: ~~~~With more rain in the forecast, and rivers at their peaks, I'm a thunk its time to start builden the Ark. Now where are those blue prints, and does any one know how much is a Cubic??
The word is actually cubit...with a T... and is the distance from your elbow to the tip of your fingers....and I have absolutely no idea why I know that
That's cuz the Coz told you, Lew.
Either that Roy or I'm just full of useless knowledge
I must be full of useless knowledge too, Lew.  Cuz I know I'm full of somethin'.
Trouble is, we don't have any gopher trees around here.
Riiiiight!   How long can you tread water?
Thinking about all the  Toronto sewage washed out into the lake
